Reiseziele entdecken & eingrenzen

As a user, I want to discover suitable travel destinations based on my preferences.
As a user, I want to compare multiple destinations to decide which one fits me best.
As a user, I want to understand how well a destination matches my expectations.

Zentrale Informationen über Reiseziele

As a user, I want to access key information about each destination.
As a user, I want to know what weather conditions I can expect during my trip.
As a user, I want to understand the general costs involved when traveling to a destination.
As a user, I want to be aware of important safety or travel-related notices.

Aktivitäten & Inhalte vor Ort

As a user, I want to learn about activities, sights, and experiences available at a destination.
As a user, I want to gain a basic understanding of the cultural aspects of the destination.

Orientierung & Visualisierung

As a user, I want to know where a destination is located geographically.
As a user, I want an intuitive way to explore and navigate through different destinations.

Unterstützung bei der Entscheidungsfindung

As a user, I want enough information to make a confident and well-informed travel decision.
As a user, I want help identifying destinations that fit within my budget.

Effizienz & Komfort

As a user, I want the planning process to be simplified and less time-consuming.
As a user, I want relevant travel information to be accessible in one place.
